At Pro Painters we do all interior and exterior services using quality products. Our services are: Walls, Ceilings(popcorn, knockdown or flat),Baseboards and trim, Door jams, Doors, Closets, Washroom, Kitchen, Cabinets, Wooden staining and all repair work. Contact us today to schedule your free consultation. 

****

During Covid-19 we are still here to answer your calls and messages and will schedule virtual appointments / walk throughs with you so we can provide quotes. I am available to use Whats App, Zoom and Video Chats to introduce myself and provide a detailed quote for any projects you're looking at doing in the future. 

****

Thanks, Mustafa
